b"Conclusion:\n\n$DCBO appears to be a good company after completing this shallow dive. I'm not going to initiate a position based on this analysis but it is a good starting point for further research."

b'Economies of scale continued

Other enterprise SaaS companies like $CRM, $WDAY, $NOW, and others have strong competitive advantages. $DCBO may have many similarities to these companies.

In the future, $DCBO may be characterized into the "enterprise SaaS" bucket.'

b'Economies of scale\n\nAs one of the larger companies in this space, Docebo can build additional product features to make their platform more competitive. Small startups can\xe2\x80\x99t offer the same number of features or the reliability of $DCBO.'

b'$DCBO is a learning management system (LMS) SaaS platform. If a company wants its employees, partners, or customers to go through training it uses an LMS platform.\n\nThink compliance, onboarding, or broad material like leadership, sales, etc.'
